[normal],
[normal] key resilience factors 
[normal]for WC pupils from most minority ethnic groups 
[normal]are high educational aspirations (both 
[normal]pupils &amp; parents), strong academic self concept and high motivation (homework)
[normal]. Th
[normal]is 
[normal]ma
[normal]y reflect the '
[normal]i
[normal]mmigrant paradigm
[normal]'
[normal] (Kao &amp; T
[normal]hompson
